.TH SSHPILOT-AGENT 1 "July 2026" "sshpilot 5.4.6" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
sshpilot\-agent \- PTY helper launcher for sshPilot local shells
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sshpilot\-agent
